  "title": "AB03 - One-to-One Coaching Tutor (Training Provided)",
  "description": "<h3>Teacher / Tutor (1 to 1)</h3><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Deliver 1 to 1 engaging lessons based on the centre’s syllabus and materials.</p></li><li><p>Teach primary / secondary / JC students (level can be adjusted based on your strength).</p></li><li><p>Provide feedback and simple progress updates to parents when needed.</p></li><li><p>Help prepare students for school exams and major exams.</p></li><li><p>Maintain a positive, encouraging and disciplined environment.</p></li><li><p>Assist with simple centre operations (e.g. admin, arranging materials) when required.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Minimum Diploma or Degree</strong> in any discipline</p></li><li><p>Able to teach at least <strong>one subject</strong> confidently: Math / Science / Chemistry / Biology / Economics</p></li><li><p>No prior teaching experience required – <strong>training will be provided</strong>.</p></li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
